overview: The Analogues, unabashedly the biggest Beatles fans on the planet, thought to themselves, "Why not record the album 'Abbey Road' at Abbey Road Studios, the actual location where The Beatles had produced it?" So they set out to do just that, and it happened on June 30, 2019.
tagline: The Analogues play The Beatle's Abbey record at Abbey Road Studios, June 30, 2019.
title: The Analogues- Abbey Road Relived
